Package: regsplice
Version: 0.2
Title: Lasso-Based Methods to Detect Differential Exon Usage
Description: Statistical methods for detection of differential exon usage (differential splicing) in RNA sequencing (RNA-seq) or microarray data sets, using L1 regularization (lasso) to improve power.
